      "description": "This folder contains all API endpoints for managing **Lists** within a board. Lists are organizational units that belong to a specific board under an organization. The following operations are supported:\n\n- **Create List** – Add a new list to a board (`POST`)\n- **Get All Lists** – Retrieve all lists associated with a given board (`GET`)\n- **Get List by ID** – Fetch the details of a specific list (`GET`)\n- **Update List** – Modify the properties of an existing list (`GET/PUT`)\n- **Delete List** – Remove a list from a board (`DELETE`)\n\nAll endpoints are scoped under `/api/v1/orgs/{ORG_ID}/boards/{BOARD_ID}/lists` and require valid organization and board identifiers."
    },
