      "description": "This folder contains all API endpoints for managing Cards within a specific List on a Board, scoped to an Organization. It covers the full lifecycle of a card, including:\n\n- **Create Card** – Add a new card to a list (`POST`)\n- **Get All Cards** – Retrieve all cards within a list (`GET`)\n- **Get Card By ID** – Fetch details of a specific card (`GET`)\n- **Update Card** – Modify an existing card's details (`PATCH`)\n- **Delete Card** – Remove a card from a list (`DELETE`)\n\nAll endpoints follow the base path: `/api/v1/orgs/{ORG_ID}/boards/{BOARD_ID}/lists/{LIST_ID}/cards`"
